{"type": "article", "id": 23807, "title": "将皮革和桦木钉起来的椅子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-14T07:00:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135005CKFMdArh06qpWzeP.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这把椅子来自以色列设计师 Ningal，采用桦木结构和经过激光切割皮革，通过 3D 打印的 ABS(工程塑料合金)接口连接，让皮革和桦木“钉”在了一起，有种手工的气质。设计师希望使用这种普通的材料使它能大范围生产，而皮革极有辨识度的颜色增加了这把椅子的时尚气息，让它很适合年轻人。<a href=\"http://www.ningaldesign.com/#!fabrics/ywcc3\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135002NbImxTlr4AGp7YZ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135003YHv4bDtJpk8nj7OR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135003osNX1qmrQuJFidfL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135004m4S1c2klynXZe3Dx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135004Kap1BuL0hIAdgENO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}